These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, water, almond-milk, iced-tea
4 different pets are kept: frog, fish, bird, pony
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, car, scooter, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the car##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
4. the person drinking tea is the owner of the frog##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
7. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | water  | iced-tea | almond-milk    | tea       |
| Pet         | fish | pony    | bird      | frog |
| Transport   | airplane   | scooter | car | taxi        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, orange, cherry, papaya
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, engineer, designer, dancer
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, quad-bike, train, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the dancer##1
2. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the designer is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the van is the coach##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | cherry   | orange | cranberry     | papaya      |
| Job         | engineer | designer | dancer | coach |
| Transport   | quad-bike    | snowmobile   | train     | van      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, reading, drawing, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, blues, disco, reggae
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, spanish, colombian, italian
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the spanish is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the fan of disco##1
5. the italian is on the right of the fan of blues##1
6. the italian is on the right of the colombian##1
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | fishing | reading | drawing | sudoku |
| Music-Genre   | reggae       | blues    | trance | disco     |
| Nationality   | thai | colombian    | italian | spanish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, lawyer, videographer, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, parkour, cycling, surfing
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, quad-bike, boat, scooter
1. the videographer is the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the lawyer is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the videographer##1
7. the videographer is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
8. the security-guard is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | scientist | security-guard | videographer | lawyer |
| Sport       | parkour     | surfing      | skateboarding     | cycling      |
| Transport   | quad-bike | van         | scooter      | boat        |

