.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, puzzles, filmmaking, gardening
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, spy, family, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, volleyball, tennis, swimming
1. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is the person watching family movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person who's hobby is photography is the person watching spy movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | filmmaking   | gardening | puzzles  | photography      |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | animation        | martial-arts  | spy       |
| Sport         | basketball | tennis    | volleyball | swimming |

