.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, bartender, police-officer, lawyer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, drama, martial-arts, epic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, techno, dubstep, d&b
1. the dressmaker is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the lawyer##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
5. the bartender is on the far left##1
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is the police-officer##1
7. the fan of techno is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
8. the lawyer is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | bartender | police-officer | lawyer | dressmaker |
| Movie-Genre   | epic   | martial-arts  | drama | time-travel   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b   | indie     | dubstep | techno       |

