.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, lime, apple, cranberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, camping, puzzles, photography
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, adventure, western, family
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
2. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is the person eating apple##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
6. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
8. the person who's hobby is camping is the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food          | cabbage  | cranberry | apple   | lime     |
| Hobby         | photography | camping   | magic-tricks  | puzzles |
| Movie-Genre   | western         | documentary  | adventure | family  |

