.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, fanta, 7up
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, scientific, martial-arts, superhero
There are 4 different nationalities: british, indonesian, brazilian, mexican
1. the person drinking sprite is the brazilian##1
2. the mexican is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the brazilian##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
6. the mexican is the person drinking fanta##1
7. the indonesian is on the left of the mexican##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | 7up | fanta     | milk | sprite |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | horror | martial-arts       | scientific    |
| Nationality   | indonesian   | mexican | british    | brazilian |

