.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, grapefruit, lettuce, nectarine
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, rock, funk, folk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, cricket, rugby, golf
1. the fan of rock is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of funk##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is the person eating grapefruit##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the fan of folk##1
6. the fan of folk is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | lettuce        | nectarine   | grapefruit  | potato   |
| Music-Genre   | indie         | folk     | rock    | funk       |
| Sport         | cricket | swimming | rugby | golf |

