.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, almond-milk, tea
There 4 different types of food: avocado, kiwi, mango, onion
4 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig, fish, snake
1. the person drinking tea is the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person eating mango is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
7. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | sprite    | almond-milk | tea | juice        |
| Food       | onion | avocado  | kiwi | mango     |
| Pet        | guinea-pig    | fish   | snake  | cat |

