.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, teacher, project-manager, journalist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, golf, badminton
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, ship, bike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the teacher##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the journalist##1
7. the person who's sport is baseball is the person driving the bike##1
8. the person who's sport is golf is the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | designer  | journalist | teacher  | project-manager |
| Sport       | golf | surfing        | badminton | baseball       |
| Transport   | van   | ship          | quad-bike          | bike       |

