.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, drawing, woodworking, collecting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, satire, sports
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, dutch, mexican, thai
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person watching sports movies is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the thai is on the left of the turkish##1
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the mexican##1
7. the thai is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | collecting   | woodworking   | skydiving | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | epic | martial-arts   | sports |
| Nationality   | thai     | turkish  | mexican  | dutch  |

