2. the person who's sport is surfing is the fan of r&b##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the fan of techno##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the fan of classical##1
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | video-games | drawing    | dancing        | fishing |
| Music-Genre   | techno     | salsa     | r&b        | classical   |
| Sport         | handball   | volleyball | surfing | rugby  |

