3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person watching drama movies is the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's sport is almond-milk-polo##1
7. the person drinking sprite is the person watching satire movies##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | sprite        | almond-milk    | soy-milk | fanta      |
| Movie-Genre   | satire        | drama   | martial-arts  | time-travel  |
