The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, biathlon, handball, parkour
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, ship, quad-bike
1. the colombian is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the dutch##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
7. the australian is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | dutch | colombian | australian | italian |
| Sport         | biathlon | swimming | parkour  | handball  |
| Transport     | bike  | motorbike | quad-bike     | ship  |

