.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, nurse, firefighter, freelancer
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, canadian, british, egyptian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, climbing, snowboarding, ice-hockey
1. the nurse is on the left of the japanese##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the firefighter##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
4. the british is on the far right##1
5. the japanese is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the egyptian is on the far left##1
7. the freelancer is on the far right##1
8. the egyptian is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | nurse  | firefighter  | manager | freelancer |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | japanese | canadian   | british      |
| Sport         | swimming | snowboarding    | climbing   | ice-hockey         |

 